features: My First Baby Doll Set - Our baby doll set is perfect for a little one that loves to take care of others! And introduce them to the world of caring and loving. Small in size, making it easy for children to hold, cuddle and carry.

18 PCS Doll Bath Toy Set - A fun set of baby shower accessories. This doll toy set includes a realistic baby doll, bathtub, bath duck, bath ball, body wash, soap, baby powder bottle, cream bottle, towel, bathrobe, potty, feeding bottle, pacifier, tableware and doll clothes set.

Realistic Pretend Play - Encourages holding, nurturing, and special care allows little ones to role-play as if caring for a real baby to enhance children's developmental and social skills during pretend play, is an excellent way to encourage imaginative play and creativity in young children.

Friendly & Safety Material - All the doll accessories are made from safe, durable, non-toxic materials, ensuring that these are safe for kids to play with. The doll toy will make 4 kinds of sounds, let your little princess enjoy the happy time of parent-child pretend role play.

Interective Educational Gift for 3 4 5 6+ Years Old - Our baby doll play set is a perfect gift for any young child who loves to play with dolls and engage in imaginative play. Also the best gift choice for Christmas, holidays, birthday or any other time.
